{
  "stem": "18626.9",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 363.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And he spoke to me in German and says, you didn't notice while you were going down that all around that cave is all machine guns lined up with SS?",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I says, no, it was too dark.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I didn't see.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But that's the truth.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "That's what it was.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "It was prepared everybody to be shot in Bad Tolz in that big cave, you know.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] how did you escape from there?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was a very difficult situation.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I saw then it start snowing and it was very cold.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And people are dying every second in the cave there.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I start to wandering around and I approached a sewer hole with a big, you know, metal on the top.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I figured, if I crawl in, in that sewer hole, it'll lead somewhere else to another opening, so I'll be out.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I slowly [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] picked up that grate from that sewer.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I start walking right into the pipes.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And it was approximately, maybe about [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] 200 feet, I start to see light.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And there was a small little village, farm village.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So that led me out right through the pipes to that little village.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I knocked in the door and a German woman, girl, opened up a little the door.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "She says in German, 'Was wollen sie denn?' I says in German, I said, please let me in.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I am hungry.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I am soaking wet.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I'm freezing.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I'm shaking.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So she opened up the door and she let me in and she let me right in the stable where the cows were all lined up and she says, hide yourself right underneath, where the cows are eating, you know.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And she covered me with hay.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
